snippet.title: Yandere Simulator's New Introduction Cutscene
snippet.description:
This cutscene would have been nothing without the phenomenal music provided by Queen Of Noise! Check out her other work here: https://www.youtube.com/user/dontforget2Bawesom/

And, equally important was the outstanding narration provided by Michaela Laws! Her channel can be found here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQTyMsas9G2_NAQkZFI-2UQ

To learn more about the game, visit https://yanderesimulator.com

For development updates, visit https://yanderedev.wordpress.com 

For cool merch, visit https://crowdmade.com/yandere

If you're concerned about rumors, visit https://yanderesimulator.com/debunk/
